    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    UK Export Finance appoints four senior trade representatives overseas
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">UKEF increases its international business development network by hiring senior trade representatives in China, Colombia, Kenya and South Africa. </p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
